# delegate()

**Instance Method**

Returns the currently assigned delegate

## Declaration

```swift
func delegate() -> Any!
```

## Return Value

Returns the current delegate, or nil if one is not set.

## Discussion

An incoming channel is one that was initiated by a remote device.
